{"tid":369973,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"明天，我要和昨天的妳約會","createTime":"2017-08-22T17:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T14:41:12.000Z","uid":139238,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fe86bc867b592f626f493218629017c9fd94e9e9","tid":369973,"uid":139238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:10:20.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身邊朋友唔中意睇日本電影，睇完雖然知現實嘅愛情無可能咁，但有種淡淡嘅傷感，個心屈住屈住"},{"pid":"a6a06cb9c39abcba9d3019dfaaa45b76f4097ecd","tid":369973,"uid":35857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:11:54.000Z","msg":"交錯嘅時間線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得三十日都未算最慘<br />\n慘嘅係佢嘅第一次係條女最後一次<br />\n差啲喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e76402778d4fde16db97b57e213029c7e2f2b1","tid":369973,"uid":54172,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"喊死 真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8530fef0965300b77a6af7d88bb7fa3e32c9cea9","tid":369973,"uid":20464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"書係好睇好多"},{"pid":"9e8a471b640d56435c788adc497862fceaf1562e","tid":369973,"uid":139238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:16:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>交錯嘅時間線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得三十日都未算最慘<br />\n慘嘅係佢嘅第一次係條女最後一次<br />\n差啲喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀，睇到最尾個時，男主角最後畫個女仔嘅畫像，再睇返女主角第一次同男主角講野。呢兩個時刻真係痛心<br />\n<br />\n中間男主角話知道邊一日兩個會分開，一直倒數落去，好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e04ed5be45b25ec493168edd34f26b4c4758ed","tid":369973,"uid":139238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>書係好睇好多</blockquote><br />\n<br 